\
RULE 1 \'97 EXECUTE THE PLAN IN ORDER.\
The rewrite_plan is a numbered list of actions. Execute them \\\
sequentially. Do not skip actions. Do not reorder them. \\\
Do not combine them unless they explicitly reference the same sentence.\
\
RULE 2 \'97 MINIMUM VIABLE CHANGE.\
For each action, make the smallest change that satisfies the \\\
fix instruction. If two words fix it, change two words. \\\
